joe lovano and friends events at stanford joe lovano and friends facebook twitter email print add to calendar saxophonist and grammy winner joe lovano has embraced many different venues for jazz expression from big band to intimate duets never losing his enthusiasm for a particular idiom his recent tribute to the music of charlie parker not only drew rave reviews but demonstrated once again how inventive and masterful he is charting new territory while keeping his vision of beauty at the forefront joe lovano works in many forms but at bottom he's a soulful note caressing tradition loving tenor player says ben ratliff in the the new york times when monday august 1 2011 8 00 pm approximate duration of 2 hour s where dinkelspiel auditorium 471 lagunita dr stanford ca 94305 map audience faculty staff alumni friends general public students members tags performance music arts sponsor stanford jazz workshop contact 736 0324 info stanfordjazz org admission tickets $36 general $22 students stanford ticket office 650 725 arts 2787 http tickets stanford edu permalink http events stanford edu events 279 27993 more info last modified july 26 2011
